HR & Admin Assistant
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/04/30 07:41:58
Ref. JB3045732
Job Description
Assisting with the day-to-day efficient operation of the HR,
Assistance and support to HR & Office Manager on a day to day basis,
Maintaining employee files and the HR filing system
Preparing offer letters, leave management, employee related letters
Handling various HR trackers, Medical insurance, stationary, office maintenance
Handling Business Visa's
Skills
Fluent English language is a must
Excellent typing skills & excel.
Minimum 2 years HR/ Admin experience
Excellent communication skills
Ability to multitask & handle stress
Team player
Excellent with follow ups
Education
HR & Admin Certificate
